* Thu Jul 05 2018 Jeanne Greulich <jeannegreulich@onyxpoint.com> - 0.1.0
- This module supports adding lists of packages to the catalog after the all
  the manifests have been compiled.  Its purpose is to support policy
  enforcement for the SIMP project and is not meant for general purpose use.
